metadata.name: Cybernetic Garden
metadata.description:
Cibernetic Gardem is a composition full of old aerials and unnatural plants, they feed on data codes produced by human communication in its different digital and analog platforms.

The work was selected for 2nd Virtual Exhibition of Contemporary Art at Escadão da Pampulha. Belo Horizonte, Brazil.

Arte no Escadão Realmix 0.2

in September 2022.
